<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,353,942,968]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Distribution.</emphasis>
Known only from 
<collectingRegion box="[590,734,942,969]" country="Papua New Guinea" name="West New Britain" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">New Britain</collectingRegion>
and Siassi Islands in 
<collectingCountry box="[1005,1232,942,969]" name="Papua New Guinea" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Papua New Guinea</collectingCountry>
(
<figureCitation box="[1253,1344,942,968]" captionStart="FIGURE 98" captionStartId="20.[151,250,1436,1460]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,956,1413]" captionTargetId="figure-372@20.[151,1436,956,1413]" captionTargetPageId="20" captionText="FIGURE 98. Distribution of the new genera and species in Malaysia, Brunei and Papua New Guinea." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6911205" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6911205/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Fig. 98</figureCitation>
: orange squares).
</paragraph>
